1. *Poverujem* ti da nisi imao nameru da me uvrediš. (I believe you didn't mean to offend me.)
2. *Poverujem* u njenu iskrenost. (I believe in her honesty.)
3. Nadam se da ćeš *poverovati* u mene kad ti kažem istinu. (I hope you will believe me when I tell you the truth.)
4. Oni neće *poverovati* dok im ne pokažeš dokaze. (They won't believe it until you show them evidence.)
5. *Poverovala* sam mu na reč i nisam proveravala. (I believed him without checking.)
6. Da li možeš *poverovati* da sam zaboravio da zaključam vrata? (Can you believe that I forgot to lock the door?)
7. Molim te, *poveruj* mi da se to nije desilo namerno. (Please believe me that it wasn't intentional.)
8. Sada *poverujem* da si u pravu. (Now I believe that you are right.)
9. Nikada ne bih *poverovala* da će se to dogoditi. (I would have never believed that it would happen.)
10. Kada mi je rekao to, nisam mogla da *poverujem* svojim ušima. (When he told me that, I couldn't believe my ears.)